# Consider what files should never be committed:
#   - Environment files with secrets (.env)
#   - Python bytecode and virtual environments
#   - Model artifacts (stored in MLflow, not git)
#   - Large data files (downloaded from Kaggle, not git)
#   - Pulumi stack configuration with secrets
#   - IDE and OS files
#   - Docker build artifacts
#   - Test coverage reports

